WEBVTT

00:03.817 --> 00:06.605
Just after 7pm she started
looking in a lot of pain,

00:06.650 --> 00:07.674
according to him,

00:07.710 --> 00:10.693
and within ten minutes,
he'd given her three injections.

00:10.710 --> 00:12.662
So you charge me
with assisted suicide

00:12.678 --> 00:14.078
and they bump it up
to manslaughter.

00:14.642 --> 00:17.650
An immediate custodial sentence
in the upper range of 8-10 years

00:17.666 --> 00:19.694
is the minimum
that should be considered.

00:19.710 --> 00:21.710
What exactly are you telling me,
Mr Schaeffer?

00:21.726 --> 00:24.650
We're just trying to locate
Mr Blakely, Your Honour.

00:24.662 --> 00:25.702
He's bolted.

00:25.718 --> 00:28.670
Well, I'm down near Gerringong,
which is not good news.

00:28.682 --> 00:29.670
Why?

00:29.686 --> 00:32.650
Because a bushwalker
just found Steve Blakely's body.

00:32.662 --> 00:33.702
Car park of the Lions Gate Hotel.

00:33.714 --> 00:35.650
Blakely and Novak?

00:35.666 --> 00:38.646
Blakely pulled this file out
two days before he died.

00:38.662 --> 00:40.638
He was going to reopen
the investigation.

00:40.654 --> 00:42.698
Oriana Vasilich.
Did Blakely have a suspect?

00:42.710 --> 00:43.718
Danny Novak.

00:43.734 --> 00:46.642
Don't fuck up what you've got
by getting involved

00:46.658 --> 00:47.698
in things
that don't concern you.

00:47.710 --> 00:49.646
What are they looking at Dad for?

00:49.662 --> 00:52.650
Because they think he killed Dianne
Vasilich's daughter, Oriana.

00:52.666 --> 00:54.706
Mr Moreno, I find you not guilty.
You're free to go.

00:54.710 --> 00:56.722
Are these photos from...
A Russian website.

00:56.734 --> 00:58.662
This is Ruby Moreno.

00:58.678 --> 01:00.839
The Vasilich family had nothing
to do with that murder.

01:01.194 --> 01:02.674
Blakely's murder's
a small part of it.

01:02.690 --> 01:04.662
If you wanna sort this mess,
ask yourself,

01:04.678 --> 01:06.682
how did Alex Moreno manage
to get acquitted?

01:06.698 --> 01:09.654
Pull out Judge Renmark's decisions
over the last two years.

01:09.670 --> 01:11.650
Why?
Something was dodgy in Moreno.

01:11.666 --> 01:14.670
I'd tread very carefully
if I were you, Ms King.

01:19.646 --> 01:21.710
They're all connected.
Blakely, Nelson, Moreno.

01:21.726 --> 01:23.678
Renmark?
Especially Renmark.

01:23.690 --> 01:25.638
He's dead.

01:25.654 --> 01:26.690
Who?
Judge Renmark.

01:26.706 --> 01:28.670
You seriously need to think

01:28.686 --> 01:30.662
about getting this Clarke guy
off the street.

01:30.678 --> 01:32.722
He's a bad man.
Get the fuck away from her!

01:33.638 --> 01:35.654
I know what you do to young girls.
You rape them.

01:35.670 --> 01:37.654
I tried to talk him out
of charging you.

01:37.666 --> 01:38.702
Doesn't matter.

01:38.718 --> 01:41.706
And the jerk is playing the victim
for all he's worth.

01:41.722 --> 01:44.674
Your Honour, I ask that this witness
be declared hostile

01:44.686 --> 01:45.966
and seek leave to cross-examine.

01:46.642 --> 01:47.654
You know he's the one

01:47.670 --> 01:49.790
who spread the rumour to the press
about you and Erin?

01:50.726 --> 01:52.682
Maya, how old were you
the first time

01:52.694 --> 01:53.934
Mr Nelson visited your bedroom?

01:54.642 --> 01:55.694
I was seven years old.

01:55.710 --> 01:57.730
He wasn't the one
creeping into Maya's bedroom.

01:58.646 --> 01:59.734
It was Dad.
You liar!

02:00.650 --> 02:02.654
He picked on me all the time.
How?

02:02.666 --> 02:04.710
Every step, I cut myself more.

02:04.726 --> 02:09.638
He didn't lift a finger.
My feet covered in blood.

02:09.650 --> 02:10.810
The feet of Blakely's corpse.

02:11.650 --> 02:13.682
Whoever killed him cut up his feet,
remember?

02:16.419 --> 02:38.113
<font color="#3399CC">Subtitles by </font><font color="ffffff">MemoryOnSmells</font>
<font color="#3399CC">http://UKsubtitles.ru.</font>

02:38.646 --> 02:39.694
It's Drew. It has to be.

02:39.706 --> 02:41.642
Just because he hated his father?

02:41.658 --> 02:42.722
You've been trying to find a
plausible explanation for the feet.

02:42.734 --> 02:44.654
This is it.

02:44.670 --> 02:46.662
The pathologist's report
was inconclusive.

02:46.674 --> 02:47.714
It can't be a coincidence.

02:47.718 --> 02:49.722
Drew's clearly
psychologically disturbed,

02:50.174 --> 02:51.694
to act as a witness
against his sister.

02:51.710 --> 02:54.646
Psychologically disturbed enough
to kill his father.

02:54.658 --> 02:55.666
Hang on, hang on.

02:55.682 --> 02:57.162
We have no forensic evidence
tying him

02:57.282 --> 02:58.682
to the murder weapon
or burial site.

02:58.698 --> 03:01.674
Not yet.
He's got a watertight alibi.

03:01.686 --> 03:03.670
Drew was on his mobile to Jack.

03:03.686 --> 03:06.642
It's hard to imagine anyone else
knocking Steven Blakely off.

03:06.658 --> 03:08.698
Hardly what you lot would call
beyond reasonable doubt though?

03:08.714 --> 03:10.674
You saw how much anger
there was in him.

03:10.690 --> 03:15.642
Now's the time to talk to him.
He's rattled. Look, family.

03:15.658 --> 03:18.018
Isn't that where the vast majority
of murders are committed?

03:18.646 --> 03:20.286
It's the first place you look.
And we did.

03:20.650 --> 03:22.682
But now you have something
you didn't have before.

03:22.698 --> 03:24.690
Look, OK, I'll bring him in
for a chat

03:24.706 --> 03:26.662
and I'll apply for
a search warrant.

03:26.674 --> 03:27.722
Thank you.

03:28.638 --> 03:32.654
Interesting business in there.
Don't expect any praise from me.

03:35.654 --> 03:37.678
Let's go. Come on.

03:41.646 --> 03:44.650
Explain to me how trashing
my reputation and Erin's

03:44.666 --> 03:46.426
was going to help you get
a favourable report

03:46.646 --> 03:47.686
on your silk application?

03:47.698 --> 03:49.710
Or did you think I'd find it funny?

03:49.726 --> 03:52.682
It was a big miscalculation
on your part.

03:52.698 --> 03:54.722
You know, it's a shame
your mate Renmark died.

03:55.638 --> 03:58.359
I could have been sacked and now
enjoying life working in a bookshop.

03:58.646 --> 04:00.654
Renmark wasn't my mate.

04:00.670 --> 04:04.650
Bullshit. He's the one who told you
I was reporting on you for silk.

04:04.666 --> 04:06.690
That was Jack Rizzoli.
Jack?

04:06.706 --> 04:08.726
You cops really look out
for each other, don't you?

04:09.638 --> 04:10.730
Was he in on the scoop too?

04:11.646 --> 04:13.726
Both have a good laugh
about the big lesbian scandal?

04:14.730 --> 04:16.706
You ever do anything
like that again,

04:16.718 --> 04:18.682
I'll make sure you lose your job.

04:20.000 --> 04:26.074
