Nelson's not going anywhere.

18:46.666 --> 18:48.706
Yes, he's appealing, but
he'll probably change his mind

18:48.722 --> 18:50.658
after a couple of days
in prison.

18:50.674 --> 18:52.694
A guy like him's not gonna
like it much.

19:10.650 --> 19:12.638
Too scared to come in
on the first lap?

19:13.702 --> 19:16.726
I don't bite,
despite everything you've heard.

19:17.638 --> 19:18.686
You don't stop, do you?

19:20.654 --> 19:22.662
You must be pleased
about the Nelson verdict.

19:22.674 --> 19:24.674
Relieved would be more accurate.

19:24.690 --> 19:26.698
But I'm sure you're not here
just to feed my ego.

19:28.714 --> 19:31.650
One of the first things
I was taught at law school

19:31.666 --> 19:34.714
was anyone who represented
themselves had a fool as a client.

19:34.730 --> 19:37.694
If I'm pleading
to this assault thing,

19:37.710 --> 19:40.674
