You sure you want to plead?

19:43.706 --> 19:46.658
Well, I hit him. Never too late
to change your plea.

19:46.674 --> 19:48.730
To what?
Defence of another.

19:49.646 --> 19:52.638
Well, he hasn't been charged
with anything.

19:52.654 --> 19:54.686
I'm not supposed to know
that he's a filthy paedophile,

19:54.702 --> 19:56.654
nor am I supposed to use
my knowledge

19:56.670 --> 19:58.190
of where he lives to go
and harass him.

19:58.638 --> 19:59.718
You've been seeing a psych,
haven't you?

19:59.734 --> 20:02.650
No-one's been telling stories
out of school.

20:02.666 --> 20:04.726
Anyone in Sex Crimes
gets dragged off

20:05.642 --> 20:07.322
