whether they like it or not.

20:07.722 --> 20:11.662
So, you get your files, and
then you do the plea yourself.

20:11.678 --> 20:13.646
It'll have much more emotional
impact.

20:13.662 --> 20:16.654
You make it all about your
panic attacks, your nightmares,

20:16.670 --> 20:18.690
