that I'm the one responsible,

21:49.658 --> 21:51.706
she's going to think that
I'm some kind of...

21:51.718 --> 21:54.726
What? A monster?

21:56.646 --> 21:59.726
I'm admitting that I took
illegal photos, alright?

22:00.638 --> 22:01.642
Isn't that enough?

22:01.658 --> 22:04.670
You'll still get a prosecution,
just without Ruby,

22:04.682 --> 22:05.718
and you'll have me as well.

22:05.734 --> 22:07.694
I think we'll stick with
what we've got.

22:07.710 --> 22:10.650
Thanks all the same.
I'm offering to plead guilty.

22:10.666 --> 22:13.642
Talk to the cops.
I don't trust cops.

22:14.646 --> 22:16.694
You want to save your daughter,

22:16.706 --> 22:19.646
you tell me everything you know.

22:19.662 --> 22:21.714
Everything. Who, what, why,
where, when, how.

22:21.730 --> 22:26.638
These people, they are dangerous.
Not my problem.

22:26.654 --> 22:28.642
Might be your daughter's,
but it's not mine.

22:28.654 --> 22:29.674
