more money.

23:33.726 --> 23:36.646
He is wasted at the DPP.
What have you got?

23:39.670 --> 23:41.678
Same as the others.

23:41.694 --> 23:44.678
Found it in a very interesting
post office box.

23:44.694 --> 23:47.654
Harvard Mark Solutions
is a business

23:47.670 --> 23:49.726
registered to one
Andrew Blakely.

23:50.642 --> 23:52.714
Drew.
He might not be running things.

23:52.726 --> 23:54.674
This just says he was involved.

23:54.690 --> 23:57.714
The USB and a bunch of disks
were in the box.

23:57.726 --> 23:59.686
They were sourced from everywhere,

23:59.702 --> 24:01.658
collated and distributed
from Russia.

24:01.674 --> 24:03.662
Well, how much material
