24:03.678 --> 24:05.706
Haven't counted exactly,
but thousands.

24:05.718 --> 24:07.722
Tens of thousands of images.

24:08.638 --> 24:10.658
Some comparatively innocent,
others...

24:11.658 --> 24:14.658
Well, torture would not be
an exaggeration.

24:14.670 --> 24:16.650
All children, wide range of ages.

24:16.666 --> 24:19.682
Until I started here, I had no idea
what sick puppies humans are.

24:19.694 --> 24:20.734
I'm with you.

24:21.650 --> 24:24.714
At least killers have the decency
to knock their victims off.

24:24.730 --> 24:28.674
So they're getting digital porn
via the post?

24:28.690 --> 24:30.678
This time, yes.
Found a mailing list?

24:30.694 --> 24:32.646
Still ploughing through
all the material,

24:32.658 --> 24:33.714
and we'll confirm who's in charge,

24:33.730 --> 24:36.638
but we can't assume it's Drew
off the back of this.

24:36.654 --> 24:37.690
What, you're thinking
Steven Blakely?

24:37.706 --> 24:40.702
Steve, Renmark, Nelson,
or maybe someone else entirely.

24:40.714 --> 24:42.650
Drew will know.

24:42.666 --> 24:44.682
Jack's personally escorting Drew
in from remand.

24:44.698 --> 24:46.706
I imagine he'll be very ready to
talk after that.

24:46.718 --> 24:49.674
Tell me about this.

24:49.690 --> 24:52.642
One of the places
Dad sourced the images.

24:52.658 --> 24:55.670
Mostly Eastern European.
