in Janet King's car.

26:12.718 --> 26:14.734
Go on.
Well, I was furious.

26:15.650 --> 26:18.722
I confronted him, and he didn't
like that. He grabbed me.

26:19.638 --> 26:23.650
We were in this car park, up high.
There was no-one around.

26:23.666 --> 26:26.690
He was dragging me over the edge.
I tried to get away from him.

26:26.702 --> 26:30.722
He was strong. And then he fell.

26:31.638 --> 26:33.670
You didn't push him?
No, I... I didn't...

26:33.686 --> 26:37.658
He was trying to push me over.
So he fell?

26:37.670 --> 26:40.690
Yeah. Or jumped, I don't know.

26:40.706 --> 26:42.722
We had a hold of each other,
and then we didn't.

26:44.670 --> 26:46.650
I didn't even hear him land.

26:54.678 --> 26:58.698
Jack said if I cooperated
you'd go easier on me.

27:06.666 --> 27:11.674
Jack, you offered Steve's killer
a deal.

27:11.690 --> 27:14.674
Well, we don't need Nelson now.
Drew's given us the lot.

27:14.690 --> 27:17.642
What the bloody hell...
Hey, hey, hey, we've cracked it.

27:17.658 --> 27:19.666
You should be at the pub.
Oh...

27:19.682 --> 27:21.722
Hey, Steve was not one of us,
OK?

27:21.734 --> 27:23.666
I know it sticks in the guts,

27:23.682 --> 27:24.718
but we've just got
to accept that now.

27:24.734 --> 27:26.730
It's only Drew's word.
No, it's not.

27:27.478 --> 27:28.678
Steve had all the right links.

27:28.694 --> 27:30.714
He was of the same vintage
as these blokes,

27:30.730 --> 27:32.718
