the same power.

27:32.734 --> 27:36.686
You can't expect a kid like Drew
to tell these guys what to do.

27:36.702 --> 27:38.674
He'd shit his pants
at the sight of anyone

27:38.686 --> 27:40.007
who was anything like his father.

27:40.642 --> 27:42.706
Guys like Steve kept
