27:42.718 --> 27:44.714
He made sure it ran smoothly.

27:44.726 --> 27:46.698
He kept the shitheads in line.

27:46.714 --> 27:48.698
He knew who to lean on
to get things happening.

27:48.710 --> 27:50.662
By blackmailing paedophiles?

27:50.678 --> 27:52.118
They're the scum of the earth,
right?

27:52.330 --> 27:54.650
Why wouldn't you lean on them?
Get them to shit themselves.

27:54.666 --> 27:56.698
Keep them in line. Get 'em
to do what you want them to do.

27:56.714 --> 27:58.690
Arrest who you want,
jail who you want.

27:58.706 --> 28:00.682
Look at it from a different
perspective.

28:00.694 --> 28:02.666
I'm not saying it's right,

28:02.682 --> 28:04.690
but the bottom line is this -
we've got him.

28:04.706 --> 28:06.730
And even without
all the theories,

28:07.646 --> 28:09.670
all the questions
have been answered.

28:20.710 --> 28:22.722
Got some news.

28:24.714 --> 28:27.718
News you need to tell me
outside of the office?

28:27.734 --> 28:31.734
Drew Blakely ran everything
under his father's guidance.

28:32.646 --> 28:33.726
Jack has a theory.

28:34.642 --> 28:37.642
Steve was blackmailing
the guys in the ring

28:37.654 --> 28:40.638
to get the results he wanted,

28:40.654 --> 28:43.678
in trials, government policy,
keeping scumbags in line,

28:43.694 --> 28:46.666
for the greater good
sort of thing.

28:46.678 --> 28:48.646
It was Steven.

28:51.670 --> 28:53.734
And what else?
What else did Drew say?

28:54.650 --> 28:55.930
Oh, looks like
he killed Renmark.

28:57.662 --> 29:00.654
After Renmark revealed
he'd organised the car bomb.

29:03.642 --> 29:04.722
Renmark?

29:08.658 --> 29:10.638
There was a connection.

29:23.646 --> 29:25.686
You know, I might not
have even been there.

29:25.702 --> 29:28.650
He didn't care if it
was just Ash and the kids.

29:29.718 --> 29:31.690
They can come home now.

29:34.702 --> 29:36.658
Yeah.

29:39.702 --> 29:41.686
Yes, they can.

29:49.730 --> 29:53.726
Hi, darling. Why aren't you
answering your phone?

29:54.602 --> 29:56.682
Look, I've got some good news
but I want to tell you,

29:56.698 --> 29:59.666
