30:13.694 --> 30:16.638
Well, I'm sure the sun
is over the yardarm.

30:16.650 --> 30:18.734
Oh, I'm sure it is. Somewhere.

30:21.714 --> 30:25.658
Ah, I'm not exactly match fit.
